quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  22,16,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ ní àwọn āyah tó yanjú. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń tọ́ ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́ sí ọ̀nà.",""
  22,17,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo àti àwọn tó di yẹhudi àti àwọn sọ̄bi’ūn àti àwọn nasọ̄rọ̄ àti àwọn mọjūs àti àwọn tó ṣẹbọ, dájúdájú Allāhu yóò ṣèdájọ́ láààrin wọn ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Arínú-róde gbogbo n̄ǹkan.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah; 2:62 àti ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yūnus; 10:90."
  22,18,"Ṣé o ò wòye pé dájúdájú Allāhu ni àwọn tó ń bẹ nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti àwọn tó ń bẹ lórí ilẹ̀, àti òòrùn, òṣùpá, àwọn ìràwọ̀, àwọn àpáta, àwọn igi, àwọn n̄ǹkan ẹlẹ́mìí àti ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ nínú àwọn ènìyàn ń forí kanlẹ̀ fún? Ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ sì ni ìyà ti kò lé lórí. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá fi àbùkù kàn, kò sí ẹnì kan tí ó máa ṣe àpọ́nlé rẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń ṣe ohun tí Ó bá fẹ́.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah ar-Ra‘d; 13:15."
  22,19,"Àwọn oníjà méjì (kan) nìyí, wọ́n ń takò ara wọn nípa Olúwa wọn. Nítorí náà, àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, wọ́n máa gé aṣọ Iná fún wọn, wọ́n yó sì máa da omi tó gbóná gan-an lé wọn lórí láti òkè orí wọn.",""
  22,20,"Wọ́n máa fi yọ́ ohun tí ń bẹ nínú ikùn wọn àti awọ ara wọn.",""
  22,21,"Àwọn òdùrọ irin (ìyà) sì wà fún wọn pẹ̀lú.",""
  22,22,"Ìgbàkígbà tí wọ́n bá fẹ́ jáde kúrò nínú rẹ̀ látara ìbànújẹ́, wọ́n á dá wọn padà sínú rẹ̀. (A óò sọ pé): “Ẹ tọ́ ìyà Iná jónijóni wò.”",""
  22,23,"Dájúdájú Allāhu yóò fi àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere wọ inú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra, tí àwọn odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. A óò ṣe wọ́n ní ọ̀ṣọ́ nínú rẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ẹ̀gbà wúrà àti àlúùlúù. Aṣọ àlàárì sì ni aṣọ wọn nínú rẹ̀.",""
